Bollore Africa Logistics May Expand Into Nigeria, Ethiopia, Echos Reports

-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 
2011-06-15T05:12:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-15/bollore-africa-logistics-may-expand-into-nigeria-ethiopia-echos-reports.html
Bollore (BOL)  Africa Logistics plans to
expand in English-speaking Africa, French daily Les Echos
reported, citing the unit’s chief executive officer Dominique
Lafont.  Nigeria, Egypt and Ethiopia are among priority countries,
Lafont told the newspaper. The unit’s African investments will
exceed 300 million euros this year, Lafont added.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  